    <title>Reflections and Vertical Stretches</title>
    <introduction>

        <list>
          <title>Student Learning Outcomes</title>
          <ul>
            <li><p>Predict how a function has been transformed by reflection or vertical scaling, given its formula.</p></li>
            <li><p>Sketch the graph of a basic function which has been transformed by reflection or vertical scaling.</p></li>
          </ul>
        </list>

